        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verses 30, 31.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - The result of the prophet's examination of the moral condition of the people. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 30.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "A wonderful and horrible thing",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", etc.; rather, ",
        "children": []
