      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "an appalling and horrible thins hath happened in the land",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The word rendered \"appalling\" (or stupefying) has a peculiar force, it only occurs again in ",
        "children": []
