        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 23:18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; not: go by their side (Ges., Dietr.), for רדה is not: go, march on, but: trample down. My people loves it so, yields willingly to such a lead; cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
